      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEDGER'S DESIRE (4) could only fill a minor placing but still clocked a dazzling 18.52 when second behind MY RUPEE at this track over 330m last start. Expected to push the clock again here. IRINKA FRED (2) box seated before sticking on well to finish 4 lengths away in second (22.87) at Dubbo in a Grade 4/5 over 400m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in the finish again. PIGEON'S DESIRE (8) goes very well this course and distance starting 74 times for 32 wins and 22 minors. In the money last time at this track (18.58) in a NG, finishing a one length third. Looks well placed here and among the chances. MY RUPEE (1) must be included in main hopes on latest effort.",
